{"tid":921303,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"4日4夜關西行程","createTime":"2018-11-29T12:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T00:32:23.000Z","uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aba8cf8879f9d13ea02f365d2f3696d900025a7f","tid":921303,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"首先我係飛凌晨機去，朝早5／6點左右到大阪，然後回程係夜晚11點，所以我預計玩足算係4日4夜既<br />\n然後我係住HOSTEL，位置係近JR福島站個邊，所以我車費方面係計住JR先（亦都懶得去計其他鐵路 都係跟GOOGLE MAP條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n因為我今次係第2次去關西，但上次去關西有少少走馬看花，所以今次去既地點唔算多但夠去就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由於D車費同路線我都係用GOOGLE MAP而佢又多數出JR比我，所以我暫時當住會用JR PASS黎玩晒呢幾日先既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外係講PLANNING之前想順便問問大阪邊到有得放行李，唔計車站LOCKER既話，我費事去到車站無LOCKER又要喪拖住黎搵，同埋LAST DAY個日都要搵地方放到去機場個陣先拎返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPLANNING如下：<br />\nDAY 1 <span style=\"color: red;\">香港－＞大阪－＞HOSTEL－＞祇園－＞鴨川－＞大阪－＞阿倍野－＞HOSTEL</span>:<br />\n大阪拎JR PASS (如果真係用JR PASS既話)<br />\n坐JR HARUKA搭到去HOSTEL (福島站)<br />\n坐JR去京橋站再坐京阪本線既出町柳特急到祇園四條站/河原町（GOOGLE MAP出比我既最快路線，預呢程會係用PASS加IC CARD搭）<br />\n去四條橋-&gt;花見小路-&gt;八阪神社-&gt;祇園-&gt;順河道行鴨川 (未去過鴨川，唔知究竟想行鴨川應該邊個位行就夠，係咪行四條橋三條橋都已經得？)<br />\n搭返車返京橋站剪頭髮，之後去阿倍野拎USJ VIP PASS+夜景入場，最後附近食野<br />\n<br />\nDAY 2<span style=\"color: red;\"> USJ全日</span>：<br />\n坐JR去USJ站，夜晚搭返JR出去梅田行下跟住食野，返HOSTEL<br />\n<br />\nDAY 3 <span style=\"color: red;\">神戶全日</span>：<br />\n搭JR去新神戶站，之後去坐纜車上布引花園，行完之後去北野異人館（聽人講主要行風見雞之館同萌黃之館就夠？）然後去三宮站，跟住落車行三宮車站－＞中心街－＞CENTER PLAZA－＞MEDITERRASS－＞元町商店街，行晒之後預計應該係下晝三四點左右，有諗過去水族館個邊睇野但好似有少少遠同唔知趕唔趕<br />\n夜晚就行去美利堅公園睇埋港塔，食完野就去東遊園地睇光之祭典，之後搭車返HOSTEL<br />\n<br />\nDAY 4 <span style=\"color: red;\">未決定</span><br />\n因為諗緊係大阪行去今昔館呀，海遊館呀，天王寺之類好無，但我怕有D係搵笨或者唔好睇<br />\n呢到想求下巴打們有無咩推介LAST DAY去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都有諗過搭去伊賀上野玩下忍者個類，但車程好似有D麻煩，所以唔知好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453dfcbc8341a7e73606065bd285e034f6c601ba","tid":921303,"uid":2300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"嘩 chur 撚到"},{"pid":"bd266f8bad85e000eaaf2e4c184903aca32cc67e","tid":921303,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"453dfcbc8341a7e73606065bd285e034f6c601ba","tid":921303,"uid":2300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"嘩 chur 撚到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"有無少少意見？<br />\n去京都嗰轉我諗住朝早去到黃昏左右應該夠時間比我行<br />\n神戶嗰個應該係有啲chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以刪減下 不過唔知chur成點"},{"pid":"bd7af6d6a473d2dd42970dd855ed495cfffe909b","tid":921303,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:35:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68dd8aac917377196542d97da3b4b54aab5f7d54","tid":921303,"uid":27609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"你自己去啊?<br />\n<br />\n我今晚都飛大阪<br />\n<br />\n要唔要哥哥帶你去飛田新地?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ef972b5b01446929748e9e30b40a00c108a56d","tid":921303,"uid":96453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"神戶乜鳩館都唔洗入<br />\n所有都伏。"},{"pid":"dc411be7a41aadd78c504022d0ecbaf13c124499","tid":921303,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68dd8aac917377196542d97da3b4b54aab5f7d54","tid":921303,"uid":27609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"你自己去啊?<br />\n<br />\n我今晚都飛大阪<br />\n<br />\n要唔要哥哥帶你去飛田新地?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T00:31:29.000Z","msg":"我下個月先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一早去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係都想試下去松島啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2587bd305fbe742e8879d2ce9aa708971328b5","tid":921303,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20ef972b5b01446929748e9e30b40a00c108a56d","tid":921303,"uid":96453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"神戶乜鳩館都唔洗入<br />\n所有都伏。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T00:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我唔去異人館淨行我上面講既其他地方得唔得<br />\n雖然我都有睇人講過異人館又貴又無野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}